1
00:00:24,540 --> 00:00:26,200
[Adapted from a novel published on Qidian Reading under China Literature]

2
00:00:26,220 --> 00:00:27,350
["Way of Choices" by Mao Ni]

3
00:00:27,940 --> 00:00:29,530
[Minors]

4
00:00:29,550 --> 00:00:31,050
[should watch with guardian consent]

5
00:02:13,660 --> 00:02:18,940
[Way of Choices]

6
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,440
Your Highness.

7
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:27,520
At last, I have you alone.

8
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,760
Ever since Your Highness crossed
the Red River,

9
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:33,640
I've been watching you in the night.

10
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,840
Born with two horns on your head.

11
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,760
You're a demon!

12
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:39,680
If the demon princess dies in
the human capital,

13
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:43,360
the alliance between humans and demons
will surely collapse.

14
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,600
When that happens,

15
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,930
it will be the day my kind march south!

16
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:52,240
Stop struggling.

17
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,680
This Smokelace Realm

18
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,440
comes from the Demon Lord's artifact.

19
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:58,160
Even a Star-Gathering Realm master
wouldn't be able to break it.

20
00:02:58,160 --> 00:02:59,890
What nonsense are you talking?

21
00:03:01,050 --> 00:03:03,520
[Falling Rain Whip]

22
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:04,600
17th on the Hundred Artifacts Ranking,
the Falling Rain Whip.

23
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:06,450
With your clogged meridians,

24
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:09,120
I could kill you within ten breaths.

25
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,730
[Emperor's Fangs]

26
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:21,060
Forcefully activating the True Essence
would be too much.

27
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,570
You brought quite a few treasures.

28
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,560
But

29
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,790
I'm still alive!

30
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,360
So, you die!

31
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,040
Darn it.

32
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,000
I wish I could use True Qi.

33
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:39,230
Star.

34
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,760
Reflect the viscera.

35
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,600
The Zhongshan Storm Sword Incantation.

36
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,800
True Essence at will.

37
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,160
Level wrist, suspend shoulder.

38
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,150
Wind and rain.

39
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:47,560
What?

40
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,720
Dou-Zhen.

41
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,250
[Dou]

42
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,760
Kui-Liu.

43
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:53,450
[Kui]

44
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,460
These are direction markers!

45
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,560
Su-Shu.

46
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,120
Tan-Wei.

47
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,280
How is that possible?

48
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,800
According to the intel,

49
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,930
with her meridians,

50
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,400
she couldn't have used the incantation,

51
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,040
let alone find out where I am.

52
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:17,839
Who?

53
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,760
Who is it?

54
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:19,640
Come out!

55
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,000
It's him.

56
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,740
My movement technique

57
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,700
is a secret from the demons.

58
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,160
Who are you?

59
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,170
How did you know?

60
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,920
Stepping on shifting star nodes,

61
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,680
there are 3,106 variations.

62
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,860
I didn't know this was the Yeshi Step,

63
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,080
but I memorized them all.

64
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,400
Fine, fine.

65
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,450
You're indeed impressive.

66
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:44,000
But Lord Black Robe has supreme wisdom.

67
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,960
He already calculated all possibilities.

68
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,920
Black Robe?

69
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,480
That most mysterious human traitor,

70
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,690
the demons' chief strategist.

71
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,760
Tonight,

72
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:55,640
all of you will die with me!

73
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,340
My five organs as sacrifices,

74
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,590
divine soul as my guide,

75
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,840
I offer my body!

76
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:04,920
Smokelace Heavenly Annihilation!

77
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,250
The Demon Lord's artifact!

78
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,320
Once it falls,

79
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,840
there'll be no hope of survival.

80
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,880
We must stop him!

81
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,160
The Demon Lord's artifact, Smokelace,

82
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,240
was once 3rd
on the Hundred Artifacts Ranking.

83
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,680
But now it's 19th

84
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:32,159
because it was once severely damaged
by an invincible master.

85
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:37,470
[Smokelace,
19th on the Hundred Artifacts Ranking]

86
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,760
So, this is an easy one.

87
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,159
You just need to use the Stainless Sword

88
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,440
to create a crack.

89
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,520
What a futile resistance!

90
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,840
Yeshi Pattern!

91
00:06:01,090 --> 00:06:03,020
You're hiding in Shendu after all.

92
00:06:03,150 --> 00:06:04,990
[Xue Xingchuan, Divine Imperial General]

93
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,760
Divine Imperial General, Xue Xingchuan.

94
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,840
I must not fall in his hands!

95
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,800
You hurt my young miss

96
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:35,390
[Jin Yulyu, Grand Steward of Baidi City]

97
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:35,400
and still want to escape through death?

98
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:40,330
I want you to regret coming to this world.

99
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:52,640
I will personally escort him
to the lowest level of the Zhou Dungeon,

100
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,080
skin him, tear his bones,

101
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,800
and interrogate him harshly.

102
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,280
No need for your concern.

103
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,080
Give me results in 3 days.

104
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:04,040
Otherwise, what happened tonight

105
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:07,570
is nothing something you,
a Divine Imperial General, can bear.

106
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,720
General Jin,

107
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,380
I'll keep that in mind.

108
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:21,240
He doesn't lose ground even when faced
with a Divine Imperial General.

109
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,680
With General Jin here,

110
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,260
she should be safe.

111
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,730
Young master, please wait.

112
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,360
You saved my young miss.

113
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:31,000
Please accept my bow.

114
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,680
In the face of the demons,

115
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,870
this is my duty.

116
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,960
This jade disc

117
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,890
can be exchanged at any bank
for 10,000 taels of gold.

118
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:38,680
No need.

119
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,400
I have to study and cultivate.

120
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:40,930
Goodbye.

121
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,200
Interesting kid.

122
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,520
Do you know what great fortune
you just missed?

123
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:53,200
East of Zhongba lies Badong Mountain.

124
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:56,360
The river cleaves a path and flows.

125
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:59,280
Baidi stands high,
guarding the Three Gorges.

126
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:02,240
Qutang is more perilous
than the Hundred Prison Pass!

127
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,440
My little Luo,

128
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,720
you recited that very well.

129
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,240
Mother.

130
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,400
When I grow up,

131
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:09,860
I want to inherit Father's Baidi City
and the 800-li Red River!

132
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,600
That's some admirable resolve!

133
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,960
Your Majesty.

134
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,540
Luoheng's meridians

135
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,760
mix human and demon traits.

136
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:23,320
I'm afraid she'll be stuck at early-stage
Star-Gathering Realm for life.

137
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:25,680
I can give you 3 years to fool around.

138
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,240
After 3 years,

139
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,520
if you can't break through
the Star-Gathering Realm,

140
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:32,179
you will marry the next heir.

141
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,450
I don't want a political marriage.

142
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:38,159
I will become the greatest Baidi!

143
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,039
Your Highness.

144
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,300
You're still injured.

145
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,560
Is he okay?

146
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,840
You mean

147
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,200
the boy next door?

148
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,200
He...

149
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,320
should be fine.

150
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,780
If he can fix my meridians,

151
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,400
he can help me change my fate!

152
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,280
Hurry!

153
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,290
I want to see him!

154
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:58,950
[Her name is Luo. She's very generous.]

155
00:08:56,850 --> 00:08:59,520
Her name is Luo. She's very generous.

156
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:01,360
[The Young Director: Episode 3]

157
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:07,280
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

158
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,080
After what happened last night,

159
00:09:08,610 --> 00:09:11,740
[Marrow Cleansing Theory]

160
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:13,060
not only did I miss the time
to absorb starlight and cleanse my marrow,

161
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,800
but I also didn't sleep well.

162
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:17,010
Thankfully, it's quiet today.

163
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,400
I must hurry and catch up
on yesterday's progress.

164
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,170
Hurry up!

165
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,120
Did no one eat?

166
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,020
You there.

167
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,450
Clear that side too.

168
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,440
This...

169
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:27,070
What's going on?

170
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:29,720
Hello.

171
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,920
Excuse me...

172
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,850
Thank you for saving me last night.

173
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,930
You're welcome.

174
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,160
It's enough that you came all this way
to thank me.

175
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,950
[Follow Your Heart]

176
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,140
Please go back.

177
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:51,960
[Cangyuan Illustration IV]
[Cangyuan Illustration V]

178
00:09:49,050 --> 00:09:50,840
These books in the box
are all unique copies

179
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,870
and very rare.

180
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:55,320
These are all herbs coveted
by cultivators everywhere.

181
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,800
As for these night pearls,

182
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:58,480
they're old relics
of the South Sea Dragon Clan.

183
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,040
Use it for night reading and cultivation.

184
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,390
They're very bright.

185
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:04,410
General Sword Codex
of the Lishan Sword Sect.

186
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:06,480
This is the secret
of the world's top sword sect.

187
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,640
Where did you copy this from?

188
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,280
Sir,

189
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,760
this is the original.

190
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:12,680
The one in Lishan Sword Pavilion
is the copy.

191
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,960
These are my gifts to seek apprenticeship.

192
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,560
I wish to take you as my master

193
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,040
and follow you in cultivation.

194
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:18,760
Master?

195
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:19,760
Why?

196
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,840
There's something wrong with my meridians.

197
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,950
Even the Tiandao Academy
and Zhaixing Academy professors

198
00:10:23,950 --> 00:10:24,950
can't resolve it.

199
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:26,280
But you can, Sir.

200
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,010
[Cangyuan Illustration IV]
[Cangyuan Illustration V]

201
00:10:27,010 --> 00:10:28,240
[General Sword Codex
of the Lishan Sword Sect.]

202
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,050
That was just coincidence.

203
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,720
Then let's spar.

204
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,080
Initiate the Canghuang!

205
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,280
True Essence through Hegu.

206
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:42,710
[Hegu]

207
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,110
[Neiguan]

208
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:44,810
Redirect through Neiguan!

209
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,360
Initiate the Canghuang!

210
00:10:53,680 --> 00:10:54,360
Sir,

211
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,760
I told you you could do it.

212
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,200
Sir,

213
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,600
please take me in.

214
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:05,280
I'll do anything you want.

215
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:06,000
Let go.

216
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,120
Let go of me first!

217
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:07,840
No!

218
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,000
Once I let go,

219
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,600
you're going to run away.

220
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:13,680
It's almost three quarters past chen hour.

221
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:15,760
So what if it is?

222
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,840
One must eat breakfast before that time,

223
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,520
or it will hurt your spleen and stomach.

224
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:20,760
Anyway, let go first.

225
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:21,720
Let go first.

226
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,120
Sir's first lesson.

227
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:25,000
[Sir's first lesson]

228
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,040
One must have breakfast
before 3 quarters past chen.

229
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,400
[Have breakfast
before 3 quarters past chen] [Bai Luoheng]

230
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,720
Sir!

231
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,650
[Porridge]

232
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,560
Strange.

233
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:38,180
Logically, the starlight I lured

234
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,980
should accumulate in my body,

235
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:42,250
like droplets gathering in a pond.

236
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,160
But

237
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,920
why is my body so empty?

238
00:12:45,530 --> 00:12:46,800
I feel nothing at all.

239
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,680
Guozi.

240
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,280
Where are you going?

241
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,120
Guozi.

242
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,520
Sorry, Sir.

243
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:06,720
You smell too good.

244
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:09,060
I dreamed I was eating
a longevity fruit.

245
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:12,640
Sir!

246
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,660
Stop following me.

247
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,520
I'm not qualified to teach you,

248
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,920
and I don't have the time.

249
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:18,860
I need to study,

250
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,760
to cultivate.

251
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:22,000
There are many important things I must do.

252
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,760
Sir,

253
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:24,550
why are you in such a hurry?

254
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,600
I want to take the Imperial Court Exam.

255
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,200
And

256
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,120
I must rank first.

257
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,320
Okay!

258
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:31,480
You...

259
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,320
Don't you think this goal is ridiculous?

260
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:34,960
At the very least,

261
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,120
you should be a little surprised.

262
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:36,960
Why?

263
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,040
If you take the Imperial Court Exam,

264
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:40,840
of course you have to rank first.

265
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,280
Anyway,

266
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:47,100
we're not on the same path.

267
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,240
Go back.

268
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:51,820
Don't come here again.

269
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:09,670
[Scripture Pavilion]

270
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,160
Earlier,

271
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,560
was I too harsh?

272
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,320
Sir, look!

273
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:02,040
We're on the same path now!

274
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:05,980
I'll come to you now!

275
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:32,690
What a rare guest.

276
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:35,400
I guessed you wouldn't last long
at the State Religious Academy,

277
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,520
but not this fast.

278
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:45,320
After listening for so long,

279
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,780
I still don't understand.

280
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,280
The State Religious Academy

281
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:51,280
is an ominous place
that defied Holy Empress Tianhai.

282
