303
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,570
It makes me envious.

304
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,080
Don't close yourself off

305
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,200
and keep people at bay.

306
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,280
More importantly,

307
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:44,240
