I have some grace.

322
00:17:24,560 --> 00:17:25,240
Let's go.

323
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,800
But I

324
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,079
kept running away.

325
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,440
I was too self-righteous.

326
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:51,560
Sir!

327
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,120
You're...

328
00:17:58,520 --> 00:17:59,650
