and the five great academies.

418
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,080
I'm not afraid.

419
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:07,000
Okay.

420
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,200
Qingteng Banquet is just the beginning.

421
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,640
Together, let's put
the State Religious Academy's name

422
